<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="268" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="7.[1441,2649,1396,2256]" pageId="7" pageNumber="268">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1443,1813,2026,2059]" pageId="7" pageNumber="268">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
CITES Appendix II. Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Kalimantan Treeshrew has probably undergone declines due to ongoing forest loss, particularly at low elevations; these declines during the past ten years are probably not large enough to warrant listing in a threatened category.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
